cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper presents a method for localizing an RGB image of a scene in a map built from LiDAR data using a Convolutional Neural Network. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV), Robotics (cs.RO), and Machine Learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE) sub-categories.
